scripts.cov: [ -z "$CODECLIMATE_REPO_TOKEN" ] && npm run cov:code-climate || npm run cov:dev
scripts.test: [ -z "$CODECLIMATE_REPO_TOKEN" ] && npm run test:simple || npm run cov:code-climate
